race.comment: LEDGER'S DESIRE (4) boasts a strong record this journey here with three wins and two minors from six tries. Comes off a (18.55) win last time, scoring by 5 lengths in a Grade 5 over 330m at this track. Appeals as a leading chance in this. ITCHY'S MAGIC (7) was in the minors two back (18.96) at this track but ran below best last time at Dubbo, finishing 6th. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. A big run wouldn't surprise. TINY MAC (1) produced a modest effort most recently when seventh at Wagga over 320m behind Oakey Lad (19.27) in a Grade 5. Was in the money prior to that. In the mix. LONE RUSTLER (2) is worth including.
